<div class="container">
  <!-- <div class="row"> -->
  <div class="panel-group" id="accordion">
    <div class="panel panel-default">
      <div class="panel-heading">
        <h4 class="panel-title">
          <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseOne">
            <strong>What is technozion Id?</strong>
          </a>
        </h4>
      </div>
      <div id="collapseOne" class="panel-collapse collapse in">
        <div class="panel-body">
          It is unique id generated for every person upon successful sign up in Technozion website.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="panel panel-default">
      <div class="panel-heading">
        <h4 class="panel-title">
          <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseTwo">
            <strong>How can I register for an event?</strong>
          </a>
        </h4>
      </div>
      <div id="collapseTwo" class="panel-collapse collapse">
        <div class="panel-body">
         Every team member should have been registered in technozion website before team registration as the technozion id is required for successful team registration
       </div>
     </div>
   </div>
   <div class="panel panel-info">
    <div class="panel-heading">
      <h4 class="panel-title">
        <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseThree">
         <strong>When will my team registration be confirmed?</strong>
       </a>
     </h4>
   </div>
   <div id="collapseThree" class="panel-collapse collapse">
    <div class="panel-body">
     Upon successful team registration, each team member should pay money 400(registration fee) + 600(accommodation(optional)) via online.<br>
     You can pay money here<p class="text-danger">Technzoion.in>>registration</p>
     Once each and every person pays the registration fee, the status of your team gets confirmed. <br>
     Sometimes due to some lags your team status might be shown pending,but you need not worry about it. Once you pay money you can come over for Technozion.
   </div>
 </div>
</div>
<div class="panel panel-default">
  <div class="panel-heading">
    <h4 class="panel-title">
      <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseFour">
       <strong>Is there any specific event registration fee for any event?</strong>
     </a>
   </h4>
 </div>
 <div id="collapseFour" class="panel-collapse collapse">
  <div class="panel-body">
    There is no separate registration fee for any kind of event. There will technozion registration fee of 400/- (per person) with which you can participate in any number of events. If you want hospitality you need to pay 600/- in order to get hospitality.
  </div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="panel panel-info">
  <div class="panel-heading">
    <h4 class="panel-title">
      <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseFive">
       <strong>What are all the ways to pay money to technozion?</strong>
     </a>
   </h4>
 </div>
 <div id="collapseFive" class="panel-collapse collapse">
  <div class="panel-body">
    You can transfer money through online to technozion. <br> There are several means to do this.
    <ol>
     <li>Credit card transfer</li>
     <li>Debit card transfer</li>
     <li>Online internet banking.</li>
   </ol>
   <p class="text-danger">WE WONT ACCEPT ANY DEMAND DRAFTS.</p>
 </div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="panel panel-default">
  <div class="panel-heading">
    <h4 class="panel-title">
      <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseSix">
       <strong>My team is registered for an event. can I change the team members now?</strong>
     </a>
   </h4>
 </div>
 <div id="collapseSix" class="panel-collapse collapse">
  <div class="panel-body">
    No.once your team id is generated you wont be able to edit your team members.
    But if you still want to change  your team members you have to cancel your team and register again as a new team.

  </div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="panel panel-default">
  <div class="panel-heading">
    <h4 class="panel-title">
      <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseSeven">
        <strong>My team registration is confirmed and we have paid technozion fee. Can I change the team members now?</strong>
      </a>
    </h4>
  </div>
  <div id="collapseSeven" class="panel-collapse collapse">
    <div class="panel-body">
     No :(
   </div>
 </div>
</div>
<div class="panel panel-default">
  <div class="panel-heading">
    <h4 class="panel-title">
      <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseEight">
       <strong>When can we expect the team registration get confirmed?</strong>
     </a>
   </h4>
 </div>
 <div id="collapseEight" class="panel-collapse collapse">
  <div class="panel-body">
   Event registrations started on 14th September, 2014 and now your are able to transfer money to technozion in order to get your team confirmed.
   Once you pay registration fee, your slot is confirmed  </div>
 </div>
</div>
<div class="panel panel-default">
  <div class="panel-heading">
    <h4 class="panel-title">
      <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseNine">
        <strong>Our team registration is confirmed and we have paid registration fee through online but we didn't apply for hospitality during that time,but we want hospitality now. what are we supposed to do now?</strong>
      </a>
    </h4>
  </div>
  <div id="collapseNine" class="panel-collapse collapse">
    <div class="panel-body">
     You can apply for hospitality here <p class="text-danger">technozion.in>>accommodation.</p> It is advised you to apply for hospitality as soon as possible as accommodation slots are limited.
   </div>
 </div>
</div>
<div class="panel panel-default">
  <div class="panel-heading">
    <h4 class="panel-title">
      <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseTen">
        <strong>Is the participation in branch events restricted to branch in which i am studying?</strong>
      </a>
    </h4>
  </div>
  <div id="collapseTen" class="panel-collapse collapse">
    <div class="panel-body">
     No. You can participate in any event irrespective of the branch in which you are studying. <br>Ex : If you are from computer science and Engg you can still participate in any event other than those from your branch 
   </div>
 </div>
</div>
<div class="panel panel-default">
  <div class="panel-heading">
    <h4 class="panel-title">
      <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseEleven">
        <strong>Do all my teammates need to be from the same college as I am or can we be from different colleges?</strong>
      </a>
    </h4>
  </div>
  <div id="collapseEleven" class="panel-collapse collapse">
    <div class="panel-body">
     You can form team consisting of people from different colleges even.
   </div>
 </div>
</div>
<div class="panel panel-default">
  <div class="panel-heading">
    <h4 class="panel-title">
      <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseTwelve">
        <strong>How do we get accommodation and food facility during Technozion?</strong>
      </a>
    </h4>
  </div>
  <div id="collapseTwelve" class="panel-collapse collapse">
    <div class="panel-body">
     Once your registration status is confirmed and you have paid money for accommodation, your/your team slot is booked for Technozion.<br>During Technozion, accommodation will be provided in the college itself starting from 16th Oct night till 19th Oct. Food will be provided from 17th Oct, 2014 morning till 19th Oct, 2014.
     <p>
     The hospitality charges are <span style="font-family:rupee;font-size:20px">R</span>600 per applicant which is inclusive of the following:
     <br>  

       <strong>Accommodation: </strong>
       <p>Accommodation would be provided in the campus hostel blocks. Participants can check-in on 16th October, 2014 5:00 pm) and they will have to vacate their allotted rooms by 20th October, 12:00 pm.</p>
       <br>
       <strong>Food: </strong>
       Food will also be provided in the institute messes which includes the following meals: <br>
       <ul>
        <li>17th October- Breakfast, Lunch and Dinner.</li>
        <li>18th October- Breakfast, Lunch and Dinner.</li>
        <li>19th October- Breakfast and Lunch.</li>
      </ul>



    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div>
